Package: pi-puck-core
Architecture: all
Multi-Arch: foreign
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, pi-puck-audio, pi-puck-boot, pi-puck-utils, pi-puck-wifi-led
Description: Pi-puck core set-up metapackage
 Installs core packages for using the Pi-puck extension board, including
 hardware set-up, and utilities for controlling devices on the board and
 attached e-puck robot.
